        <updateDate>2015-05-22T15:21:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Same Day Registration Act</b></p> <p> Amends the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to require states with a voter registration requirement to make same-day voter registration available at the polling place on the date of election itself (or on the day of voting under early voting).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
